law.history: Repealed 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 325, sec. 37, effective July 13, 1990. -- Created 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 257, sec. 22, effective July 15, 1980.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: No bonds to be issued except on approval of capital projects and bond oversight committee, interim joint appropriations and revenue committee or standing appropriations and revenue committee.
